"title": "8299: love, in relationships",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8299",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Human love is ennobled by being patterned on God's love for his people. It is also safeguarded by God's commands.</p>\n<h2>The love between husband and wife</h2>\n<h3>Conjugal love is commanded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:18-Col3:19\">COL 3:18–3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:5\">DEU 24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:18-Prov5:20\">PRO 5:18–5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:9\">ECC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:22\">EPH 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:28\">EPH 5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:33\">EPH 5:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:7\">1PE 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>It is patterned on God's love for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:5\">ISA 54:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:25–5:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:5\">ISA 62:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:14\">JER 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:8\">EZK 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:19\">HOS 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2\">2CO 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:7\">REV 19:7</a></p>\n<h2>The power of human love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:6-Song8:7\">SNG 8:6–8:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:20\">GEN 29:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:30\">GEN 29:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:34-Prov6:35\">PRO 6:34–6:35</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of love in courtship and marriage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:67\">GEN 24:67</a> <em>Isaac and Rebekah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:18\">GEN 29:18</a> <em>Jacob and Rachel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:4\">JDG 16:4</a> <em>Samson and Delilah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:5\">1SA 1:5</a> <em>Elkanah and Hannah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:17\">EST 2:17</a> <em>Xerxes and Esther</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:2\">SNG 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:10\">SNG 4:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:1\">HOS 3:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:19\">MAT 1:19</a> <em>Joseph and Mary</em></p>\n<h2>Safeguards on human love</h2>\n<h3>Sexual immorality is condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:2\">1CO 7:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:22\">LEV 18:22</a> <em>homosexual acts forbidden</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:29\">LEV 19:29</a> <em>prostitution forbidden</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:17-Deut23:18\">DEU 23:17–23:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:32\">MAT 5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:29\">ACT 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:26-Rom1:27\">ROM 1:26–1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:1\">1CO 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18\">1CO 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:8\">1CO 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5\">COL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3\">1TH 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>Adultery is condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:14\">EXO 20:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:10\">LEV 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:18\">DEU 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:24\">PRO 6:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9\">1CO 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>Restrictions on divorce</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:9\">MAT 19:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:16\">MAL 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:32\">MAT 5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:11-Mark10:12\">MRK 10:11–10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:18\">LUK 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:10-1Cor7:11\">1CO 7:10–7:11</a></p>\n<h3>Lust is condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:28\">MAT 5:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:1\">JOB 31:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:25\">PRO 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:9\">1CO 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:19\">EPH 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:5\">1TH 4:5</a></p>\n<h3>Polygamy is forbidden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2\">1TI 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:17\">DEU 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:15\">MAL 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:12\">1TI 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:6\">TIT 1:6</a></p>",
